Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.52,0:01:36.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}在不論勝敗之地我們相遇
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.48,0:01:40.49,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}描繪又擦去
